.TH SHUTDOWN 8
.SH NAME
shutdown \- shut down system/emulator
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B shutdown
.B -h
.PP
.B shutdown
.B -r
.SH DESCRIPTION
.I Shutdown
halts
.RB ( -h )
or restarts
.RB ( -r )
.IR emu (1)
or a native kernel.
If restarted,
.IR emu (1)
will be given the same options as were given it when it started.
.SH FILES
.B /dev/sysctl
.SH SOURCE
.B /appl/cmd/shutdown.b
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.IR cons (3)
